data.description: Welcome to 3101 NW 47th Ter Unit #423. Opportunity awaits in this spacious 2 bed, 2 bath condo nestled in the serene ALL AGES Cypress Chase community of Lauderdale Lakes. Situated on the top floor, enjoy tranquil water views from your screened balcony. With a washer and dryer conveniently tucked in-unit, and central A/C, this home offers modern convenience. This community features assigned parking, guest parking and amenities galore. Don't miss out on this chance to customize and make it your own! Call today to schedule a tour!
